Description:
Description:
It should be possible to create documents related to this Vreemdeling.

Solution:
create a tab Document with the functionality to fetch information of all these MBES18 tabs and records.
This in done in all rol/proces and also in Arrestanten module.

Testplan:
Step 1: Go to Opsporing - MBES18
Step 2: Enter a new record in MBES18 module, fill in the required fields and click save.
Step 3: Go to tab Documenten and generate a document
Step 4: This document should contain the same values in the MBES18 record

Navigation:
Opsporing - MBES18 -Tab Documenten
